title: Ep. - 307 - BRIAN MOYLAN BRAVO AND REALITY SHOW BREAKDOWN
description:
Author Brian Moylan helps Kate review Bravo shows including Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, Orange County, Potomac, and Atlanta, and Southern Charm. Brian also advises Kate on what new British reality shows to watch and Kate suggests what he should binge on his vacation back to the States.
